systemback (1.7.302) release; urgency=low

  * 1.7.302
  * Fix a temporary initramfs file deletion
  * Bump year numbers
  * Import some fixed Russian translations

  * 1.7.301
  * Some translations updates and fixes

  * 1.7.300
  * Add lupin-casper support to the generated loopback.cfg file
  * Add lupin-casper to the recommended packages on 64-bit systems
  * Import new Czech translations

  * 1.7.200
  * Fix some operation errors when a file name contains garbage characters
  * Add auto line break to some terminal outputs
  * Import new French and Danish translations

  * 1.7.101
  * Fix some Live operations when the working directory path is contain a space
    character
  * Import new German translations

  * 1.7.100
  * Add debug levels for the error messages
  * Create /usr/bin/systemback-sustart symlink
  * Do not allow to start the CLI when the stderr is redirected; print the error
    messages to /tmp/systemback-cli_stderr when a process has stopped because an
    error occurred
  * Do not format the redirected standard outputs
  * Redirect the stdout and stderr to /dev/null when starting a silent process
  * Always copy the latest SB configuration files when necessary
  * Do not update the systemback.conf file if not necessary
  * Auto choose the original filesystem for selected partitions
  * Do not allow to set a custom mount point when an existing file
  * Fix partition unmounting when the path contains a space
  * Fix the storage dir mount point checking in some cases
  * Fix some file deletion when copying the system without formatting
  * Fix Live create when a partition is mounted under user home dir
  * Fix the error message printing when a partition table cration is failed
  * Fix the segmentation fault when compiled with Clang
  * Fix hardening-no-relro lintian warnings
  * Update the Debian manuals
  * Update UEFI boot files
  * Import new Romanian and Brazilian Portuguese translations

